Se Mi, not Kim Yeong Ran.

420
00:32:33,500 --> 00:32:34,477
Bu Se Mi?

421
00:32:34,501 --> 00:32:38,143
Yes, a graduate from Iseon Women's University's
Early Childhood Education department.

422
00:32:38,167 --> 00:32:40,809
Born in 1994. Raised in Gangnam.

423
00:32:40,833 --> 00:32:43,276
Father's a professor.
Mother runs an art gallery.

424
00:32:43,300 --> 00:32:45,909
