I don't have a dad.

823
00:59:08,133 --> 00:59:10,343
But, you have

824
00:59:10,367 --> 00:59:12,576
an amazing dad

825
00:59:12,600 --> 00:59:15,500
who loves only you.

826
00:59:16,233 --> 00:59:18,809
I really envy that.

827
00:59:18,833 --> 00:59:20,443
That's true.

828
00:59:20,467 --> 00:59:23,033
My dad's the best.

829
00:59:25,233 --> 00:59:28,633
He's truly wonderful, right?

830
00:59:30,633 --> 00:59:34,243
Miss, I'm leaving now.

831
00:59:34,267 --> 00:59:35,867
Okay.

832
00:59:39,367 --> 00:59:41,576
Goodnight.

833
00:59:41,600 --> 00:59:43,533
Sleep well.

834
00:59:50,600 --> 00:59:52,476
Sleep well.

835
00:59:52,500 --> 00:59:54,600
You too, Miss.

836
01:00:06,522 --> 01:00:09,624
[Sujeong Hotel]

837
01:00:15,500 --> 01:00:17,733
[Ms. Bu Se Mi]

838
01:00:23,867 --> 01:00:25,376
Madam.

839
01:00:25,400 --> 01:00:28,043
It seems that the situation
might be resolved easily.

840
01:00:28,067 --> 01:00:29,676
What do you mean by that?

841
01:00:29,700 --> 01:00:32,109
Ga Seon Woo has something significant.

842
01:00:32,133 --> 01:00:36,176
If we secure that, your exile will end.

843
01:00:36,200 --> 01:00:38,276
Mom came to Muchang.

844
01:00:38,300 --> 01:00:40,609
Ah, so she went there.

845
01:00:40,633 --> 01:00:42,809
Attorney Lee, what do you mean by that?

846
01:00:42,833 --> 01:00:45,043
You knew all along and didn't contact me?

847
01:00:45,067 --> 01:00:47,409
Kim So Yeong isn't
important right now, madam.

848
01:00:47,433 --> 01:00:49,076
Don't forget

849
01:00:49,100 --> 01:00:51,233
how much this game is worth.

850
01:01:08,600 --> 01:01:10,967
Where did he throw it?

851
01:01:27,567 --> 01:01:29,633
Darn it.

852
01:02:25,300 --> 01:02:27,167
It's been a while.

853
01:02:29,767 --> 01:02:32,267
I contacted you because I need a favor.

854
01:03:36,200 --> 01:03:40,067
[20-19, Eumjeon-ro 28beon-gil, Muchang-my
eon, Muchang County, Gyeongnam]

855
01:03:51,833 --> 01:03:59,833
[Professor, I'll handle it soon]

856
01:04:33,033 --> 01:04:38,567
♫ Starting to be born again ♫

857
01:04:51,233 --> 01:04:53,776
♫ Now is the time ♫

858
01:04:53,800 --> 01:04:57,376
I want to look into the background of
someone who previously worked here.

859
01:04:57,400 --> 01:04:59,143
Seon Woo, where are you right now?

860
01:04:59,167 --> 01:05:00,743
Again, again, again!

861
01:05:00,767 --> 01:05:02,043
Sis, don't you remember that day?

862
01:05:02,067 --> 01:05:03,843
I'll just send this to Kim Yeong Ran.

863
01:05:03,867 --> 01:05:06,309
We might end this game
quickly without bloodshed.

864
01:05:06,333 --> 01:05:07,676
She changed her identity?

865
01:05:07,700 --> 01:05:09,743
If Kim Yeong Ran dies now,
it'll complicate things.

866
01:05:09,767 --> 01:05:11,243
Why did you follow me last night?

867
01:05:11,267 --> 01:05:12,443
Are you spying on me?

868
01:05:12,467 --> 01:05:16,233
Then if that woman dies
instead of Kim Yeong Ran...

869
01:05:17,567 --> 01:05:21,500
Maybe it wouldn't be such a bad thing
for someone else to die.
